OL,3,CCharity praises bank for new debt
OL,4,Ccollection approach and improved
OL,5,Ccustomer help
OL,7,FHSBC UK has been awarded an "advanced"
OL,8,Fmental health accessible rating by a
OL,9,Fcharity set up by Martin Lewis after
OL,10,Fthe bank improved customer digital
OL,11,Fsupport and tested new approaches to
OL,12,Fdebt collection.
OL,14,FThe Money and Mental Health Policy
OL,15,FInstitute said its assessment took
OL,16,Finto account the design of HSBC UK's
OL,17,Fproducts and services as well as the
OL,18,Faccessibility of digital platforms.
