OL,4,Ccollection approach and improved
OL,5,Ccustomer help
OL,7,FThe advanced rating is the second of
OL,8,Fthree levels that firms can achieve
OL,9,Fthrough the programme.
OL,11,FThe accreditation reflects steps HSBC
OL,12,Fhas taken in recent years, the charity
OL,13,Fsaid, including trying out different
OL,14,Fapproaches to debt collection such as
OL,15,Freducing the frequency of
OL,16,Fcommunications to some customers about
OL,17,Fdebts. Money and Mental Health's
OL,18,Fresearch suggests this could result in
OL,19,Freduced stress for customers.
