OL,7,FHSBC UK's "chat with us" function in
OL,8,Fits app can also identify certain
OL,9,Fvulnerable situations through the
OL,10,Fwords a customer uses.
OL,12,FThis may lead to tailored help, such
OL,13,Fas referring customers to digital
OL,14,Fsupport from the bank's specialist
OL,15,Fteams.
