OL,4,Ccollection approach and improved
OL,5,Ccustomer help
OL,7,FHelen Undy, chief executive of the
OL,8,FMoney and Mental Health Policy
OL,9,FInstitute, said: "In particular, we're
OL,10,Fpleased to see the bank testing new
OL,11,Fapproaches to debt communications
OL,12,Fwhich have the potential to decrease
OL,13,Fstress for customers and deliver
OL,14,Ffinancial returns for the bank `
OL,15,Fbanks, building societies and utility
OL,16,Ffirms should take note."
OL,18,FFaye Byrne, head of supported banking
OL,19,Fat HSBC UK, said: "Our focus is on
OL,20,Fremoving barriers that can add stress
OL,21,Fat difficult times."
