OL,7,FThe programme was established after
OL,8,Fresearch by Money and Mental Health
OL,9,Findicated that people with mental
OL,10,Fhealth problems face serious
OL,11,Fdifficulties when engaging with
OL,12,Fessential services.
OL,14,FThe Money and Mental Health Policy
OL,15,FInstitute was set up by Mr Lewis to
OL,16,Fhelp break the link between financial
OL,17,Fdifficulty and mental health problems.
